Project License Notice
======================

This repository contains:
1) Build/tooling code in this repository (scripts, Makefile, styles, plist metadata).
2) Dictionary source data obtained from an external provider (ISLEX).

The legal terms for (2) are not overridden by this repository.

Data License Summary (Important)
--------------------------------
The lexical data pipeline depends on ISLEX, the Icelandic-Scandinavian
multilingual dictionary distributed under Creative Commons
Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-ND 4.0)
by Stofnun Árna Magnússonar í íslenskum fræðum / CLARIN Iceland.

Under CC BY-NC-ND 4.0, generated dictionary bundles must be treated as
derivative, non-commercial-only outputs of the licensed data.

Practical compliance guidance:
- Allowed: local/private building and personal, non-commercial usage with attribution.
- Not allowed: redistributing modified source data.
- Not allowed: redistributing compiled .dictionary bundles produced from ISLEX data.
- Not allowed: any commercial use.
- This repository therefore ships only build tooling — never compiled
  .dictionary bundles, and never a copy of the ISLEX XML itself.

You are responsible for verifying current terms at the original data source.
If source licensing changes, update this notice and your distribution behavior.

